      "side": 1,
      "message": "This option is being displayed on Toro/PrimeC instead of \"LTE/CDMA\" as it is without this change. It is confusing to see this in the \"Mobile network setting -\u003e Network Mode\" menu option and then see \"LTE/CDMA\" and \"CDMA\" on the dialog box. This is because of the \"preferred_network_mode_values_lte\" at line 410 below.\n\nI\u0027m wondering if this should simplified from the user perspective and if they should just be given a choice of 4g/3g/2g/1g ?",
      "revId": "583ba1595c5acefb36d5a179a48730806542392a",
      "serverId": "85c56323-6fa9-3386-8a01-6480fb634889",
      "unresolved": false
